@startuml seq-11-semantic-search
title POST /search/semantic — vector similarity over chunks

actor "User" as U <<human>>
participant "Browser" as B <<browser>>
participant "Express\n/search" as API <<service>>
participant "authenticateToken +\nrequireDocLibraryAccess +\nrequireUseAiQueries" as MW <<service>>
participant "embedQuery\n(Gemini)" as G <<external>>
database "PostgreSQL\n(vectorSearch)" as DB

B -> API: POST /search/semantic\n{ query, limit? }

API -> MW: chain
alt Blocked / invalid
  API --> B: 401 / 403 / 400
else OK
  API -> G: embedQuery(query)
  alt Invalid embedding / no API key
    API --> B: 503 or error
  else OK
    API -> API: build vecLiteral + deptIds\n(admin vs readableDepartmentIds)
    API -> DB: $queryRaw vectorSearch\n(accessFilter on READY chunks)
    DB --> API: ChunkRow[]
    API --> B: 200 { query, results[] }
  end
end

note right of API
  Source: **apps/api/src/routes/search.ts** (~96+),
  **embeddings.ts** (**embedQuery**).
end note

@enduml
